{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6435", "repo": "rails", "body": "@drogus @yahonda seems I cannot edit this pull request, I create a new one here: https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6439\n\nI don't suggest revert this: 'lazy_load_hooks' is not used in activesupport/lib/active_support/dependencies/autoload.rb, there's no reason load it there.\n\nactivesupport/lib/active_support/i18n.rb use and load it, but i18n.rb itself is conditionally loaded through autoload.\n\nSince lazy_load_hooks.rb defines methods about ActiveSupport itself, I think it should be reasonable to load it in lib/active_support.rb.", "_id": {"$oid": "52380848bd3543c15100cbee"}, "issue_id": 6435, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5847603", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6435#issuecomment-5847603", "updated_at": "2012-05-22T13:57:34Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janx/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janx/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janx/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janx/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/janx", "login": "janx", "gravatar_id": "8853f712852b03ba6646b59b1723f44d", "html_url": "https://github.com/janx", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janx/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janx/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janx/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/8853f712852b03ba6646b59b1723f44d?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F8fdd149fcaa7058caccc9c4ad5b0d89a.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janx/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 5958, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/janx/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2012-05-22T13:57:34Z", "id": 5847603, "owner": "rails"}
